Problimataki: Parousiazetai to e3is: otan estw kai 1 gonidio enos atomou den exei plastikotita perimenei olos o pli8ismos
gia na ginei mature. Mipws na baloume ena orio oti meta apo x "genies" an den exei ginei mature to sigkekrimeno atomo
kane ton delete?

To problima entinetai an baloume 10 gonidia gia ton ka8ena kai o pli8ismos einai ena sebasto noumero. Den sizitaw gia 
100.000 pou legame stin arxi. Dokimasa me 400 atoma kai 10 gonidia ston ka8ena kai iparxei periptwsi
na min ginei pote mature olos o pli8ismos.(Ta ma8imatika epali8euoun oti den einai aparaitito na emfanistei plastikotita pantou)

Exei mpei ena orio 50.000 "genies" gia maturity olou tou pli8ismou se periptwsi pou to 3eperasei kanei exit to programma giati 
meta apo ekei mou kremage olo to pc. (Laptop tou 2004 den mporei na ante3ei)

Kata ta alla me mikrotera noumera ola douleuoun.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

8ewritika to programma prepei na trexei kai gia megalitero pli8ismo. Me tin parousa ilopoihsh ka8e fora pou tsekarw
tin plastikotita katanalwnw O(n^2) , opou n o ari8mos twn "genarations" pou exoun perasei mexri twra. 
An pame gia megalo ari8mo "geniwn" tote 8a prepei na allaxei drastika to olo programma kai na brw kalitero tropo gia na
apo8ikeuontai ta nea gene_counts tis ka8e genias.Pros to paron mpainoun se mia single-linked list.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Episis ta perissotera optimizations pou kikloforoun einai gia megalous pinakes (1000x1000) kai den nomiza oti 8a doume diafora
an pame kai kanw optimize auto to simeio ka8ws oi pinakes pou pollaplasiazoume einai arketa mikroi (10x1 * 10x1)

Proxwrisa ligo parapera kai brika kommati kwdika pou ipologizei apostasi metaxi 2 pinakwn.
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/12398689/how-to-calculate-distance-between-two-matrices-in-c
8a to xrisimopoihsw gia to otan ginei o pli8ismos mature na ipologisw tin diafora tou apo to optimal.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

I have done the following assumptions as of now:
To optimal array (-1 ews 1) logika den einai proswpiko gia to ka8e atomo.
Stin parousa ilopoihsh opoios emfanisei plastikotita stamataei na "e3elissetai".
Assumptions correct or not?
